---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="section" style="min-height: 100vh; padding-top: var(--space-24);">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <a href="/" style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: var(--space-8); color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: var(--text-sm);">&larr; Back to Intelligent Economics</a>

      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-2xl); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">Last updated: April 16, 2026</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">What we collect</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">When you submit a form on this site, we collect the information you provide: name, email address, location, area of expertise, availability, selected roles, and any optional message. We also record the date and time of submission.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">How we use it</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Your information is used solely to:</p>
      <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-4); padding-left: var(--space-6); list-style: disc;">
        <li>Contact you about volunteer opportunities matching your skills</li>
        <li>Send project updates (if you opt in)</li>
        <li>Aggregate anonymous statistics about our volunteer base (e.g., "40% of volunteers are economists")</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">We will never sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Form processing</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">Form submissions are processed by <a href="https://www.netlify.com/products/forms/" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Netlify Forms</a>, which securely stores submissions and delivers them to our team. Netlify's privacy policy governs their handling of data.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Analytics</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">We use <a href="https://plausible.io/" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Plausible Analytics</a>, a privacy-respecting analytics service that:</p>
      <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6); padding-left: var(--space-6); list-style: disc;">
        <li>Does not use cookies</li>
        <li>Does not collect personal data</li>
        <li>Does not track users across sites</li>
        <li>Is fully compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Cookies</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">This site does not set any cookies.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Third-party services</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">This site loads resources from:</p>
      <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6); padding-left: var(--space-6); list-style: disc;">
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Fontshare</strong> — Web fonts (Clash Display, Satoshi)</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Plausible</strong> — Privacy-respecting analytics</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Netlify</strong> — Hosting and form submission processing</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Your rights</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6); padding-left: var(--space-6); list-style: disc;">
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Access</strong> any personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Correct</strong> inaccurate data</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Delete</strong> your data from our records</li>
        <li><strong style="color: var(--color-text);">Withdraw</strong> consent at any time</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-6);">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:Rob@theoradical.ai" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Rob@theoradical.ai</a>.</p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-top: var(--space-10); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Contact</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--space-16);">For privacy-related questions, contact <a href="mailto:Rob@theoradical.ai" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Rob@theoradical.ai</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
